<li id="cite_note-11"><b><a href="#cite_ref-11" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://findarticles.com/p/articles/mi_m1568/is_n2_v26/ai_15473457" class="external text" title="http://findarticles.com/p/articles/mi_m1568/is_n2_v26/ai_15473457" rel="nofollow"><i>Reason</i>, June 1994</a></li>
