<li id="cite_note-14"><b><a href="#cite_ref-14" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.ted.com/index.php/talks/kary_mullis_on_what_scientists_do.html" class="external free" title="http://www.ted.com/index.php/talks/kary_mullis_on_what_scientists_do.html" rel="nofollow">http://www.ted.com/index.php/talks/kary_mullis_on_what_scientists_do.html</a></li>
